{"tid":1705680,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【11・11各區衝突】警射海綿彈　一男右眼受傷","createTime":"2019-11-11T02:20:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T02:39:16.000Z","uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"877f763ac57d63376fba51366cb347ecbd35c7bb","tid":1705680,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T02:20:46.000Z","msg":"本港多區今日（11日）早上開始出現衝突，示威者於旺角彌敦道一帶以雜物堵路，其間一位女士因推開示威者的路障與示威者發生口角，其後有人向她面部噴黑漆。警方於旺角拘捕至少4男1女。<br />\n<br />\n在觀塘，一批防暴警察於apm商場及港鐵觀塘站A出口與示威者對峙，警方突然衝前噴射胡椒噴霧，示威者退至apm組成傘陣，不久後離開，防暴警察繼續於該處築成防線。<br />\n<br />\n上水廣場小巴總站外，被搜出V煞面具的男子被警方帶走。有市民在附近天橋上往下倒水，警員向天橋位置發射海綿彈，一名男子右眼受傷。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20191111/s00001/1573436047617/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191111%2Fs00001%2F1573436047617%2F&d=UQnAMLTNR8x1T2wYrkOS%2BAy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=da9310a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191111%2Fs00001%2F1573436047617%2F&h=3b01dfaa\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20191111/s00001/1573436047617/</a>"},{"pid":"dfc0006a36a6238282eb88fc8f5fb2d66436a851","tid":1705680,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T02:21:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"618ddc4e723511e655dc9b3dedccbdc3b2e0e3d9","tid":1705680,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T02:24:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32727389c739832742f9758e79286768e3c98b0d","tid":1705680,"uid":249263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T02:27:16.000Z","msg":"最新：tag左英國議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/lukedepulford/status/1193698691212828673?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flukedepulford%